* Continental breakfast served - 8:30 - 9:00 AM
* Keynotes - 9:00 - 10:00 AM
* Lunch - 12:15 - 1:15 PM 
* Closing Remarks - 5:00 PM

=== Wednesday, January 23, 2013 ===
* Continental breakfast served - 8:30 - 9:00 AM
* Lunch - 12:15 - 1:15 PM 
* Closing Remarks - 5:00 PM
* Evening Reception at the Country Inn & Suites - 6:00 - 8:00 PM

