== Venue and Travel Information ==

=== Venue ===

This latest in the [[OVirt_Global_Workshops|Global Workshops Series]] will be hosted by NetApp at their [http://goo.gl/maps/KK7y8 Corporate Headquarters] in Sunnyvale, California, USA. Attendees will need to check in at Building 7 upon arrival.

