For attendees who wish to book a hotel room, we have secured a room block at the nearby [http://goo.gl/maps/csHQT Country Inn and Suites] at a room rate of 125 USD / night for a standard room and 145/night for a king suite, excluding tax and incidentals. To book into the hotel room block, please phone +1.408.747.0799. 

